feels.name: Determination
feels.quote: Ahab's hawser tows his purpose yet.
feels.place: On the deck of the ship

feels.name: Desperation
feels.quote: Ahab never thinks; he only feels, feels, feels; that’s tingling enough for mortal man!
feels.place: On the deck of the ship

feels.name: Resignation
feels.quote: Ahab is for ever Ahab, man. This whole act’s immutably decreed.
feels.place: On the deck of the ship

feels.name: Concern
feels.place: On the deck of the ship

feels.name: Confusion
feels.quote: The Parsee—the Parsee!—gone, gone? and he was to go before:—but still was to be seen again ere I could perish—How’s that?
feels.place: On the deck of the ship

Places.name: Deck_of_the_ship
Places.description: The location where the characters are interacting and experiencing various emotions.
